                            Nifty Index
                        </div>

                        <div id="NiftyIndexClosePrice" class="mb-0 font-weight-bold text-gray-800" style="font-size:14px">Close Price :</div>

                        <div id="NiftyIndexDate" class="mb-0 font-weight-bold text-gray-800" style="font-size:14px">Date        : </div>
